    Q7 -- Yes --> Q8{8. Operator accepts<br/>12–18 month durability window<br/>+ re-fine-tune cycle?}
    Q8 -- No --> Halt[/Single-train assumption<br/>not supported by data<br/>do not proceed/]
    Q8 -- Yes --> GO([Execute recipe<br/>GRPO + SFT-distillation +<br/>reliable LLM-judge +<br/>9-layer self-hosted inference])

